data.description: Come look at this cute 3 Bedroom 2 Bath located in the amazing Blue ridge school district. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms. Roof replaced in 2013 with architectural shingles. HVAC 2016. This home sits on over a half acre lot with mature trees creating a beautiful wooded view.Less then a mile away from Greenville Technical College and very close to Lowes and Target.The house is 15 mins from downtown, 5 mins from Paris Mountain, and 30 mins to Jones Gap State Park. Enjoy your own fire pit while entertaining your family and friends in a park like setting. Nice and quiet neighborhood. Both the storage buildings stay. Seller to offer $5000 credit which can be used towards changing the floors or closing cost.
